title: Tria Deli
typeOfFood: Lacto, Western, Salad bar, Take-out, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small salad and sandwich cafe on a lively street. Offers around 15 veggie salads stored in a refrigerator separate from any meat. Ranges from pasta, couscous, and potato salad to beans and chickpea to vegetables like spicy cauliflower, red cabbage with pine nuts. Very filling.
